<br>
I went in with a tank and a helper in the bar room and just had the tank bring in constant pulls until the goblin spawned- also ended up with some Drake Hide leggings. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ubaedm.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Baedm</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif  BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/16/00 4:25:58 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=103.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.facelink.com/B8065?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Goblin</span><hr size=1> It's been a while since I did this quest, but there are some things I've very certain of regarding Sol A.<br>
<br>
1) My Heart dropped off of a High Inferno Goblin Wizard.<br>
2) He was close to the Lavastorm zone, not far from the Goblin Foreman (I didn't go very deep from that zone).<br>
3) He wasn't that tough compared to the other Inferno Goblins.<br>
<br>
When I camped the King Area for Bard armor quests I killed numerous mobs and I never saw a heart drop in that area.  You won't find it there. <p><BR>
<A HREF="mailto:baedm@hotmail.com">Baedm Solarrian</A>  [ <A HREF="http://www.telusplanet.net/public/cawolf">Order of Legends</A> ] -- <A HREF="http://www.portice.com/berthall">Bertoxxulous</A><BR><i>Take it slow.  Premature Evocation could happen to you!</i></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/utelegareth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Telegareth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/16/00 9:42:27 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=103.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Infernal wizard</span><hr size=1> Woot finished the quest last night in about four hours total.<br>
<br>
Had a lambent stone already, so a guildmate and I decided to go to SolA for the heart.  He's a lvl 35 mage and needed the fire gobbie skin, so we killed two birds with one stone. Entered SolA and proceeded to the Barroom which was being camped by one person.  Since all we wanted was a heart and skin, we stayed, <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> , very nice guy too.  got a call from another guildmate so we rounded up a small party of four, myself, mage, chanter, and druid.  Sat in the barroom killing everything for about an hour to an hour and a half when poof, the wiz spawned right beside me, hehe, got the heart of fire.<br>
<br>
Off to permafrost, the mage and I ran there and first stop was to collect the rod for the staff of the wheel, then into permafrost after collecting the ice giant toes for the mage quest.  We go into prmrfrost and make a wrong turn, end up in the &quot;king room&quot;. One person there again, camping the king, another really nice guy, who had just killed a wiz, tried to loot the corpse, but it had decayed, Oh well, at least I know they spawn in there, <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .  The mage, myself, and the other player killed the trash in the king room till &quot;poof&quot; wizard spawns right near me, (must have been medding, hehe).  Dead wizard, get the heart, <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Stuck around to see the king die, and kill some of the elite guards for xp, got another wiz to spawn but saw no king.  <br>
<br>
Off to lake rathe to get the rod of bone, easy to do, the pet was no match for the mage's pet, and we nuked the skellies, got the rod.<br>
<br>
Port into Nek, and run to the temple, got my staff, a very fun quest, gave me some time to chat with a guildmate I don't get to group with a lot and I finally made it to halas as a High Elf Wizzie, <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Sorry for the long post, had to share the excitement with the rest of you <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udaeanorendarion.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Daeanor Endarion</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.monmouth.com/~dhawthorne/everqst/picon.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/17/00 11:24:55 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=103.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.monmouth.com/~dhawthorne/everqst/ppic.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Infernal wizard</span><hr size=1> There is an intersection just before the bar; the rooms right and left from there often have Inferno wizzies, as well as right in that hall way at times. They also spawn in the small rooms off the room to the right of the bar, one of which also spawns the drunkard and his clarity potion. The other area the IW's pop is near the Efreeti area, and near the CWG. <p><b>Daeanor Endarion of the Rathe</b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ukamasutra3.showPublicProfile?language=EN>KamasuTra3</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/17/00 8:39:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=103.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Infernal wizard</span><hr size=1> Arg, I camped the Heart of Fire with a 52 pally friend for 3 hours and never saw one. Went ot the bar room the enitre time. No one was around so we just tore up the zone and got no loot except the clarity potion. /sigh. I only need the heart of fire, maybe one day I'll see one.... <p><center><img src="http://www.negative-net.com/kamsig.jpg"></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umonoriu.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Monoriu</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/17/00 10:09:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=103.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Inferno goblin wizard</span><hr size=1> My experience:<br>
<br>
Day 1, spent 2 hours killing everything near the bar, nothing. No inferno goblin wizard.<br>
<br>
Day 2, spent 2 hours killing everything in the bar. One inferno goblin wizard spawned, no heart.<br>
<br>
Day 3, I logged on, went straight to SolA, invis up, ran straight to the bar......there he was, inferno goblin wizard. One ice comet, hes dead, and he got the heart.<br>
<br>
/shrug<br>
<br>
Keep trying <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uasiago.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Asiago</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/17/00 11:52:57 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=103.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.spacehotel.com/images/asi_icon.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Inferno goblin wizard</span><hr size=1> Yea, the  bar is a good place.  I too had no luck for many levels and finally at level 50 went into Sol A by myself for the last part of the flux staff quest.  I cleared spawn in the bar, the adjacent rooms and the drunkard room.  Basically one ice comet per goblin.  If you stay far enough back you can pick them off one by one at lvl 50.  There seem to be several inferno spawns.  The wizard spawned in one of the bar customer spawn spots and had the heart.  Finally!<br>
<br>
The wizards don't seem to spawn a whole lot tho, so be patient. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udaeanorendarion.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Daeanor Endarion</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.monmouth.com/~dhawthorne/everqst/picon.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/18/00 9:50:41 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=103.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.monmouth.com/~dhawthorne/everqst/ppic.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Inferno goblin wizard</span><hr size=1> I camped them once for an entire Sunday afternoon - about 6 hours - and we saw a total of 3 inferno wizards, and none dropped the heart (though I did get the drunkard's clarity potion). The same day a friend was camping the CWG and picked up a heart right after I gave up, so we joint-quested to finish it. The wizards are uncommon at best, and the heart drop the same. <p><b>Daeanor Endarion of the Rathe</b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uvdiyan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vdiyan</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://wwp.icq.com/scripts/online.dll?icq=15325080&img=5 BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/19/00 8:34:56 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=103.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.multimania.com/thoane/Vdiyan.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Inferno goblin wizard</span><hr size=1> Hello,<br>
